        {
            "title": "聯儲會主席鮑威爾計畫出席美國最高法院就庫克案舉行的聽證",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 一位知情人士透露，<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:聯儲會;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/聯儲會\">聯儲會</a>主席傑羅姆·鮑威爾計畫出席美國最高法院周三就總統唐納德·川普試圖解職聯儲會理事麗莎·庫克一案舉行的聽證。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">去年10月，最高法院曾拒絕允許川普在庫克提起訴訟以保住職位期間立即將其解雇。這項裁決意味著庫克可以繼續留任，至少在最高法院本周聽取口頭辯論並作出裁決之前。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普在8月下旬以未經證實的抵押貸款欺詐指控為由下令解職庫克，庫克已否認相關指控。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">聯儲會觀察人士和法律分析人士表示，該案的結果將對總統解職聯儲會理事的能力產生深遠影響，並進而影響央行在不受政治干預情況下制定利率的能力。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-dcd6ad93-4bda-324e-bc1d-acbff2c3e217-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">鮑威爾計畫出席此次聽證由美聯社最先報導，在他上周表示美國司法部已向聯儲會發出大陪審團傳票之後，這一動向更具分量。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此前，鮑威爾似乎一直避免發表可能激怒總統的公開言論。在12月10日的記者會上被問及庫克案時，他選擇不予回應，表示：「我們不是法律評論員。案件仍在審理中。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Fed’s Powell Plans to Attend Cook’s Supreme Court Hearing</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Amara Omeokwe.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%81%AF%E5%84%B2%E6%9C%83%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD%E9%AE%91%E5%A8%81%E7%88%BE%E8%A8%88%E7%95%AB%E5%87%BA%E5%B8%AD%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98%E6%B3%95%E9%99%A2%E5%B0%B1%E5%BA%AB%E5%85%8B%E6%A1%88%E8%88%89%E8%A1%8C%E7%9A%84%E8%81%BD%E8%AD%89-205702162.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-20 05:30:45",
